* Clear Start Times (Gun & Chip)
* When to use:    Before a new race or during testing to quickly reset start time data for all participants.
* How to use:     Double-click to run the file. It will automatically execute the macro to clear both fields.
* Note:           This macro can clear any other database field (e.g., Age, DNF, Wave, Division).
* Customize:      Comment out (*) either line if you only want to clear one specific field, or add extra fields if needed.


clear-f.rsm GunStart
clear-f.rsm ChipStart